aa(lp90
VAnd when people ask me, "Are these words real?"
p91
aVI had a variety of answers that I tried out.
p92
aVSome of them made sense. Some of them didn't.
p93
aVBut one of them I tried out was,
p94
aV"Well, a word is real if you want it to be real."
p95
aVThe way that this path is real because people wanted it to be there.
p96
aa(lp97
V(Laughter)
p98
aa(lp99
VIt happens on college campuses all the time.
