aVThe problem with that is,
p128
aVno one seems to know what those two letters stand for.
p129
aa(lp130
V(Laughter)
p131
aa(lp132
VWhich is kind of weird, right?
p133
aVI mean, it could be a misspelling of "all correct," I guess,
p134
aVor "old kinderhook."
